body:
The following reduced test case:
```Verilog
module top;
    function automatic [23:0] func;
        input [23:0] in;
        func[21+:7] = in[21+:7];
    endfunction
    initial $display("%b", func(24'h060708));
endmodule
```
Crashes on master with:
```
Assertion failed: (val.size() == wid), function of_RET_VEC4, file vthread.cc, line 5475.
```

Bisecting identifies ce9f3d5e591b38814d2f6a1b01fe337ae25908dc as introducing the issue.

